title: Trump’s New Social Media Platform Is Already A Disaster - Leftovers #5
description: On this episode of Leftovers the boys discuss if sex work is work, why people say all cops are bad, and Trump's brand new social media venture (twitter close) is absolutely demolished within hours of being announced!
